{"tid":1590972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際/支那戰線] 白人警叫亞裔示威者做 Yellow Object","createTime":"2019-09-24T03:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T05:10:03.000Z","uid":24178,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa27328b5b1311bc0a16cbb4de319a29346ae6fb","tid":1590972,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:19:43.000Z","msg":"試想一下:<br />\n如果係美國有個黑衫既黑人示威者俾人打完後叫佢做black object<br />\n你會聯想到佢講件衫定講個人?<br />\n同樣地諗點解大家會解得呢位啊sir 係講緊件黃背心唔係講緊黃皮人?<br />\n<br />\ntwitter/reddit 同我煲大佢呢個就一定<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要</span>係煲大陸戰線<br />\n連儂/wechat/藍絲群 先係重點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地強大既中國人俾人叫做黃色物件</span><br />\n我唔知你地點反應 (曲)<br />\n但我就碎到一地都係 <br />\n無論你支持定係反政府我地都係黃皮膚<br />\n呢啲係我地圍內既事<br />\n點輪到你啲白人係到說三道四<br />\n前場指揮官又係白人<br />\n出來羞辱香港人又係你班白人<br />\n極度懷疑根本警隊就一早俾外國入侵左<br />\n要求成立獨立調查委員會!<br />\n還香港白警一個清白"},{"pid":"2d64b7a455afd93b5c816beeba60310742e8bd7b","tid":1590972,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:19:56.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"293fe7ac3fd6c49149973cb3f44fa9fb495cc469","tid":1590972,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:20:52.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7520fd01595df8b188cd19f06a82d3c842da91ff","tid":1590972,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ac30b9858ace108dc741d2cea5d03e452555cb17","tid":1590972,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:21:12.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"5a01270f7cfc7fe95a5ebc12032a29eccb489857","tid":1590972,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"047c26cb30f99139bf8cff3bb82d806f64dc0ec4","tid":1590972,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"6362c5c21c3cf465b3237f5856ba94362fb892e4","tid":1590972,"uid":24178,"like":